{"tid":1393957,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【遍地開花】  號召醫學生以其名義 參與罷工罷課集會","createTime":"2019-08-01T09:09:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T09:25:34.000Z","uid":240968,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"93fbfc39868282af9254448c133153f8ce0c3047","tid":1393957,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:09:06.000Z","msg":"個人立場<br />\n<br />\n其實班做staff咗嘅哥哥姐姐佢地好想罷工，無奈醫護係專業，唔似黑警話走就走，如果佢地罷工，影響力雖大，但維持病人生命嘅醫療程序可能受影響，一班受傷示威者亦有機會因為無曬班尊從medical ethics，緊守崗位嘅醫護前線而落單。<br />\n<br />\n但佢地用盡一切辦法，做文宣，組織FA 支援，竭力守護香港人既自由同健康，甚至<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有護士因去前線做FA 被告暴動罪</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n咁我地醫護學生呢？我發夢都見唔少示威者/FA都係讀醫護既大學生。<br />\n<br />\n但8月2號/8月5號罷工集會各行業遍地開花，當醫護界既Staff 根本無可能大規模罷工，我地係咪更應該用醫護學生既身份，代staff咗嘅哥哥姐姐集會行出黎聲援醫學界，比社會知 除左班某院藍絲前線高層，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>仲有一班良心醫護支持五大訴求，支持社會公義同自由</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n除左港大醫護搞罷課集會，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解仲未有各大專醫護組織響應集會？？？</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n在此，我呼籲<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n1) 大專醫護組織響應8月2 號愛丁堡罷工集會/ 8月5號三罷<br />\n<br />\n2) 讀緊醫護既學生著住制服/白袍（無就黑tee+PPE），帶證，用醫學生嘅身份聲援醫學界出席民間集會<br />\n<br />\n3) 開設屬於全港醫護學生既TG group </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n同時，Staff 咗嘅哥哥姐姐，allied health workers，我絕對支持你地用唔同方式，出席集會，帶黑口罩、黑絲帶番shift，去宣示立場支持五大訴求。<br />\n唔好怕，我地一班醫學生一定會支持你地。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n一個成日發夢既護士學生上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OGAGD4p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOGAGD4p.jpg&h=9e04304b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"781b626a300f6e8abe13f21a56cc9fcedec5e22f","tid":1393957,"uid":240968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:10:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Eyti6b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Eyti6b.jpg&h=aaabbd49&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v129NZA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv129NZA.jpg&h=b4f19b0b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d2Tti6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd2Tti6f.jpg&h=b0319352&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6OgiGjA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6OgiGjA.jpg&h=bb1807ee&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qX2qmjA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqX2qmjA.jpg&h=be8a61d6&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aYROi6g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaYROi6g.jpg&h=f574f1e4&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uNQ0acW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuNQ0acW.jpg&h=f7858164&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dw9kacY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdw9kacY.jpg&h=ec9fe91d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i8zwgSY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi8zwgSY.jpg&h=01a65e41&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kprZqMj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkprZqMj.jpg&h=09b250d6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39d586519d337c0075b1f67b633c1e738496e3c7","tid":1393957,"uid":240968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:11:34.000Z","msg":"《港大醫護 不平則鳴 &ndash; 港大醫學院學生八月五日罷課不罷學運動聯署聲明》<br />\n<br />\n我們已草擬八月五日罷課集會之聯署聲明，當中包括集會同學之五點立場。構思中集會內容包括籌辦First-aid workshop（由有經驗人仕教授前線救援知識或準備醫療包等）<br />\n<br />\n各位同學如認同集會理念，以及會參與當日集會，請填妥以下Google Form加入聯署。<br />\n<br />\n星期一見！<br />\n<br />\n(English version of the statement will be available soon)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/ScE4pTnu8fyjZPqs8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FScE4pTnu8fyjZPqs8&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl5z8W653rZVWOX%2F4zqp%2BjK3Y%3D&h=6a07ebcb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/ScE4pTnu8fyjZPqs8</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Db5CWTr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDb5CWTr.jpg&h=3a27867b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wsDEqMN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwsDEqMN.jpg&h=43195e1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u5cFadt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu5cFadt.jpg&h=57a57a14&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c98c86547999a4684349058eb408b802a11073b1","tid":1393957,"uid":240968,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:11:59.000Z","msg":"&lt;醫護人員的心聲&gt; 正因為醫護人員要堅守崗位，<br />\n我地懇請更多香港市民代我地參與罷工！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1379247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1379247</a>"},{"pid":"154ec87653c3734ef6182a5e7daa1c4e73884d0b","tid":1393957,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:13:01.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab80b84ffdcf8971e497bc23becef6ff9756bc7c","tid":1393957,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:13:21.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8073c9074c5fd486df16cd7f93368d105b3dad41","tid":1393957,"uid":240968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:13:32.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6